Define a function 

that ask  user "Say something here !: "
ask user  to "Enter a number: "
Store the  user's  answer from "Say something here !: " based on user's input number as an index position in the given list below as shown as in the result.
my_list=["yes","no","yes","no","yes","no","no"]

















my_list =["yes","no","yes","no","yes","no","no"]

def insert_index():
    x = input ("Say something here !: ")
    y = int(input ("Enter a number: "))
    my_list.insert(y,x)
    print (my_list)
